snippet.title: Atomic Heist Release Trailer
snippet.description:
See more at http://www.atomicheist.com releases on April 20!

Grab the atomic core and fight your way out of the overrun space station. Manage your ammo carefully. Use collected power ups wisely. The core is leaking radiation so move quickly. Along the way unlock permanent items and find secrets to ease the escape and pull off the Atomic Heist.
